OL,3,CInquest investigates if factory worker
OL,4,Cwho died was exposed to toxic gas
OL,6,FA coroner has finished questioning
OL,7,Fwitnesses at an inquest into the death
OL,8,Fof a factory worker who collapsed
OL,9,Fwhile at work, possibly after being
OL,10,Fexposed to poisonous gas.
OL,12,FAlexander Reginald Cole, 71, died in
OL,13,Fhospital on Christmas Day 2021 after
OL,14,Fhe was found unconscious at the
OL,15,FFutamura plant in Wigton the previous
OL,16,Fmorning.
OL,18,FThe court heard how he was discovered
OL,19,Fin the site's pump house by Robert
OL,20,FDyer, an HGV driver who had arrived
OL,21,Ffor a delivery.
