OL,3,CInquest investigates if factory worker
OL,4,Cwho died was exposed to toxic gas
OL,6,FMr Cole was lying on the floor with
OL,7,Fblood coming from his head.
OL,9,FShortly after raising the alarm, Mr
OL,10,FDyer also lost consciousness and was
OL,11,Fremoved from the room by a colleague.
OL,13,FEvidence from witnesses recalled a
OL,14,Fstrong odour of rotten eggs inside the
OL,15,Fpump house.
OL,17,FMr Cole was taken to the Cumberland
OL,18,FInfirmary where he died following
OL,19,Fmultiple cardiac arrests.
