OL,3,CInquest investigates if factory worker
OL,4,Cwho died was exposed to toxic gas
OL,6,FAn investigation by the Heath and
OL,7,FSafety Executive (HSE) focussed on the
OL,8,Fpotential presence of hydrogen
OL,9,Fsulphide gas in the pump house on the
OL,10,Fmorning Mr Cole was found.
OL,12,FHydrogen sulphide (H2S) is a
OL,13,Fcolourless but toxic gas which is a
OL,14,Fbyproduct of some processes that occur
OL,15,Fat the Futamura plant. It has a strong
OL,16,Fodour similar to that of rotten eggs.
