OL,3,CInquest investigates if factory worker
OL,4,Cwho died was exposed to toxic gas
OL,6,FInvestigator Jason Wan told the court
OL,7,Fthat, while no conclusive evidence
OL,8,Fexists of the presence of H2S on that
OL,9,Fmorning, he had identified two ways in
OL,10,Fwhich the gas could have entered the
OL,11,Froom via the drainage system.
OL,13,FEvidence from Cumbria Fire and Rescue
OL,14,Fidentified the presence of H2S in the
OL,15,Fpump house later on the same day.
OL,17,FMr Wan's investigation concluded that
OL,18,FH2S was present in the pump house on
OL,19,Fthe morning of 24 December 2021.
