OL,3,CInquest investigates if factory worker
OL,4,Cwho died was exposed to toxic gas
OL,6,FEvidence from Mr Cole's GP stated that
OL,7,Fhe had a history of cardiovascular
OL,8,Fdisease.
OL,10,FDr Julia Capper, who was on shift when
OL,11,FMr Cole arrived at the hospital, told
OL,12,Fthe court that she couldn't say what
OL,13,Fhad caused the cardiac arrests with
OL,14,Fany degree of certainty.
OL,16,FEvidence from toxicologist Dr Paul
OL,17,FSmith said that there is no
OL,18,Ftoxicological test available in the UK
OL,19,Fto identify H2S.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
