OL,3,CInquest investigates if factory worker
OL,4,Cwho died was exposed to toxic gas
OL,6,FDr Fergus Young, who performed a post-
OL,7,Fmortem examination of Mr Cole, told
OL,8,Fthe court he believed it was probable
OL,9,Fthat Mr Cole had been exposed to a
OL,10,Ftoxic gas which led to cardiac arrest.
OL,12,FThe coroner is expected to make a
OL,13,Fverdict on the cause of Mr Cole's
OL,14,Fdeath in the coming days.
